@page
@model FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<!-- Hero – uniform bg -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-14 lg:py-20 dark:bg-slate-800/40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full border border-subblue-200 bg-subblue-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-subblue-700 dark:border-subblue-700 dark:bg-subblue-900/40 dark:text-subblue-300">Support</span>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 lg:text-4xl dark:text-slate-100">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Answers to common questions about Subchron time tracking and attendance.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ accordion – answers hidden until user clicks -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-12 lg:py-16 dark:bg-slate-800/40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="space-y-3">
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    What is Subchron?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Subchron is a workforce time tracking system for organizations that need accurate recording of employee attendance in physical on-site environments. It supports QR scanning, biometrics, overtime management, and payroll/ERP integration.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    Who can use Subchron?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Organization Administrators and HR Staff manage employees and schedules. Supervisors and Managers approve overtime and validate attendance. Employees record time-in and time-out via QR or manual entry. Payroll Personnel export approved data for payroll processing. System Vendor/Super Administrator has full access.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    How does time capture work?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Employees record time-in and time-out at on-site stations using QR code scanning or manual entry. The system validates on-site attendance and maintains attendance logs. Overtime is identified from configured schedules and approved by supervisors.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    Can I export data for payroll?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Yes. Subchron provides approved attendance and overtime data via RESTful API endpoints and CSV files. External payroll or ERP systems can consume this export-only data for processing.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    Is my data secure?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Subchron uses role-based authentication and authorization, input validation to prevent incorrect data, audit logging for all actions, and session management for secure user access. Data is stored securely and access is controlled by roles.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800/90 dark:ring-slate-700">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                    How do I get started?
                    <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-slate-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-slate-600">
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Choose a plan (Basic, Standard, or Enterprise), configure your attendance mode (QR, Biometric, or Hybrid), add employees and stations, set schedules and policies, then start recording attendance. See <a asp-page="/HowItWorks" class="font-semibold text-subblue-600 hover:text-subblue-700 dark:text-subblue-400 dark:hover:text-subblue-300">How It Works</a> for the full flow.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Still have questions?</p>
            <a asp-page="/Landing/Contact" class="btn-primary-glow mt-4 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-subgreen-500 to-subgreen-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 dark:from-subgreen-500 dark:to-subgreen-600">Contact us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
